  "content": "<p data-pid=\"4XSJ_OIE\">推荐个 <b>Anki</b>：</p><p data-pid=\"PLc6sb76\">Anki 是一个能够<b>记笔记</b>、以<b>自测</b>的形式复习、有复习安排<b>算法</b>的软件。</p><p data-pid=\"UpEhX3lc\">用 Anki 复习笔记是这样的：</p><p data-pid=\"Tzv8XYNa\">英语：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f04355834b9e08e011112296a825913b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"405\" data-original-token=\"v2-f04355834b9e08e011112296a825913b\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f04355834b9e08e011112296a825913b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;405&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"405\" data-original-token=\"v2-f04355834b9e08e011112296a825913b\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-f04355834b9e08e011112296a825913b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f04355834b9e08e011112296a825913b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/><figcaption>下面四个选项就是算法安排的时间</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"F8tD_EIO\">生物：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6ed0a51dda80c542074bde1862e8c968_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"298\" data-original-token=\"v2-6ed0a51dda80c542074bde1862e8c968\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ed0a51dda80c542074bde1862e8c968_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;298&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"298\" data-original-token=\"v2-6ed0a51dda80c542074bde1862e8c968\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ed0a51dda80c542074bde1862e8c968_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6ed0a51dda80c542074bde1862e8c968_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/><figcaption>左边是正面，右边是反面</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"0dn6AvcF\">化学：<br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e37c9fab26738849547b8a66268fcbef_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"540\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-e37c9fab26738849547b8a66268fcbef\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"540\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e37c9fab26738849547b8a66268fcbef_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;540&#39; height=&#39;960&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"540\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-e37c9fab26738849547b8a66268fcbef\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"540\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e37c9fab26738849547b8a66268fcbef_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e37c9fab26738849547b8a66268fcbef_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/><figcaption>没错，有手机端</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"e8FhixT7\">Anki 会详细记录每一条笔记的复习（自测）情况：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b045d200d75a27ca36af58ab4d9adc85_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"775\" data-original-token=\"v2-b045d200d75a27ca36af58ab4d9adc85\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b045d200d75a27ca36af58ab4d9adc85_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;720&#39; height=&#39;775&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"720\" data-rawheight=\"775\" data-original-token=\"v2-b045d200d75a27ca36af58ab4d9adc85\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"720\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b045d200d75a27ca36af58ab4d9adc85_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b045d200d75a27ca36af58ab4d9adc85_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"UkX6_40G\">我高二到高三用 Anki 记了 1 万 5 千多条笔记：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c52678bca7cb1ee5c7a6b2a215de082f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1035\" data-rawheight=\"931\" data-original-token=\"v2-c52678bca7cb1ee5c7a6b2a215de082f\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1035\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c52678bca7cb1ee5c7a6b2a215de082f_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1035&#39; height=&#39;931&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1035\" data-rawheight=\"931\" data-original-token=\"v2-c52678bca7cb1ee5c7a6b2a215de082f\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1035\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c52678bca7cb1ee5c7a6b2a215de082f_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c52678bca7cb1ee5c7a6b2a215de082f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"K4dayyWQ\"><b>还没高三</b>的同学可以上手试试（高三的同学还是别刷知乎了）</p><p data-pid=\"a--nm7af\">下面是我高考前的统计数据：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1665\" data-rawheight=\"3420\" data-original-token=\"v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1665\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1665&#39; height=&#39;3420&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1665\" data-rawheight=\"3420\" data-original-token=\"v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1665\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"8V--NAHa\">Anki 相关的认知科学理论：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"uB7dx-5B\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57020308\" class=\"internal\">间隔重复</a></li><li data-pid=\"-f4mGKBT\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57113246\" class=\"internal\">测试效应</a></li><li data-pid=\"VphxvwnK\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57139724\" class=\"internal\">穿插练习</a></li></ul><hr/><p data-pid=\"rt4W_xu2\">Anki 支持 windows、mac、linux、安卓、苹果等常见设备，并且可以多端同步，走到哪学到哪。</p><p data-pid=\"ER7md9xJ\">为了帮到有缘人，我写了一份快速上手教程：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2e8a109841199b0a18e70ae7bd16ea66_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1220\" data-image-height=\"535\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：B 站 Ankidroid 视频教程与电子书(全平台教程)快速通道</a>",
